---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noimageindex" />
    <title>Christophe Bernard - CV</title>

    <style>
        @import "tailwindcss";

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background: #fff;
            color: #111;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .header {
            /* Handled by Tailwind flex classes */
        }

        .header-content {
            /* Handled by Tailwind flex-1 class */
        }

        .photo {
            width: 110px;
            height: 110px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            /* margin-left handled by Tailwind */
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .header h2 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin: 4px 0 10px;
            color: #444;
        }

        .contact {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .hero {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .hero ul {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            padding-left: 16px;
            list-style-type: disc;
        }

        .section h3 {
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .job {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .job-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .job-sub {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .job ul {
            margin: 4px 0 0 0;
            padding-left: 16px;
            list-style-type: disc;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .block {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .block ul {
            margin: 4px 0 0 0;
            padding-left: 16px;
            list-style-type: disc;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        @media print {
            body { margin: 0; }
            .container { margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div class="header flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row md:justify-between items-center sm:items-start">
        <div class="header-content flex-1 text-center sm:text-left">
            <h1>CHRISTOPHE BERNARD</h1>
            <h2>Staff Engineer / Product-minded Tech Lead</h2>
            <div class="contact">
                Paris • Remote worldwide<br>
                christophe.bernard@gmail.com • +33 6 67 24 54 46<br>
                chris-bernard.github.io • github.com/chris-bernard
            </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/cv-photo.jpg" alt="Christophe Bernard" class="photo mb-4 sm:mb-0" />
    </div>

    <!-- VALUE -->
    <div class="hero">
        Engineer with 20+ years of experience helping startups and scale-ups
        build the right product before building it right.<br><br>

        I combine product thinking, pragmatic architecture and fast execution
        to avoid wasted development and accelerate time-to-market.

        <ul>
            <li>Built products from 0 → first customers</li>
            <li>Strong product + engineering bridge</li>
            <li>Experience across startup, scale-up and enterprise</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- FLEXBOX CONTENT -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:gap-10">

        <!-- LEFT -->
        <div class="section md:w-2/3">

            <div class="block">
                    <h3>EXPERIENCES</h3>

                    <div class="job">
                        <div class="job-header">
                            <span>Datalok — Product Advisor</span>
                            <span>2024–2025</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="job-sub">Datacenters marketplace (early-stage) - Pre-PMF</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Took product from 0 → 5 paying clients</li>
                            <li>Structured product positioning and user feedback loops</li>
                            <li>Defined UX, roadmap and iteration cycles</li>
                            <li>Bridge between founders, product vision and engineering</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="job">
                        <div class="job-header">
                            <span>Independent Projects & Product Strategy</span>
                            <span>2022–2024</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="job-sub">Entrepreneurial exploration</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Built and structured a coaching activity for freelancers</li>
                            <li>Developed content strategy and audience on LinkedIn</li>
                            <li>Explored multiple product ideas (SaaS, marketplaces)</li>
                            <li>Continuous exploration of AI, LLM workflows and MCP</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="job">
                        <div class="job-header">
                            <span>Malt — Staff Software Engineer</span>
                            <span>2021–2022</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="job-sub">Europe's leading freelance marketplace - Series C funding</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Led initiatives improving freelancer acquisition and experience</li>
                            <li>Contributed to product decisions impacting conversion and retention</li>
                            <li>Aligned engineering execution with product and business goals</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="job">
                        <div class="job-header">
                            <span>Wegrow — First Engineer / Tech Lead</span>
                            <span>2018–2021</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="job-sub">Early-stage SaaS - From pre-PMF to seed</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Built SaaS platform from scratch (architecture + delivery)</li>
                            <li>Owned roadmap, prioritization and delivery cycles</li>
                            <li>Combined engineering leadership with product decisions</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="job">
                        <div class="job-header">
                            <span>Gaston Services — First Engineer</span>
                            <span>2017–2018</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="job-sub">B2C automotive SaaS (early-stage) - Pre-PMF</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Built full product (customer app, ops, backoffice)</li>
                            <li>Designed event-driven architecture (event sourcing)</li>
                            <li>Contributed to product design via event storming</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="job">
                        <div class="job-header">
                            <span>Homework.chat — First Engineer</span>
                            <span>2015–2016</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="job-sub">EdTech startup (early-stage) - Pre-PMF</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Built early version of a tutoring marketplace (students ↔ teachers)</li>
                            <li>Explored business model and product positioning</li>
                            <li>Designed and implemented fullstack architecture (API + frontend)</li>
                            <li>Delivered MVP and iterated on early user feedback</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="job">
                        <div class="job-header">
                            <span>Earlier Experiences</span>
                            <span>2006–2015</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="job-sub">Postions in Software Engineering and Delivery</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Architecture & tech lead roles in large-scale systems</li>
                            <li>Sale and distribution of travel services (Amadeus, SNCF Connect) & Banking (Natixis, Société Générale CIB)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>

        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT -->
        <div class="section md:w-1/3">

            <div class="block">
                <h3>CORE EXPERTISE</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Engineering:</strong> Architecture, APIs, event-driven systems</li>
                    <li><strong>Tech:</strong> Java, Spring, TypeScript, Angular</li>
                    <li><strong>Product:</strong> Discovery, MVP, roadmap</li>
                    <li><strong>AI:</strong> LLM workflows, MCP</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="block">
                <h3>WHAT I BRING</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Challenge what should be built</li>
                    <li>Connect business, product and engineering</li>
                    <li>Strong pre-product-market fit experience</li>
                    <li>Pragmatic: speed of learning over perfection</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="block">
                <h3>EDUCATION</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>IMT Mines Alès — Engineering</li>
                    <li>Université Paris XI — Economics</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
